  "detailed_description": "Choose your Ninja team and embark on a quest through the wilderness to seal away the spirits of evil and save your village. Fight through procedurally-generated nature dungeons in turn-based battles driven by action commands. Collect pearls during your runs and spend them in the village to unlock new teams, upgrades, and information about the monsters you face.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694230/extras/eff4238cd08dfba998b958fc9b7cb58f.poster.avif?t=1767451782\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694230/extras/eff4238cd08dfba998b958fc9b7cb58f.webm?t=1767451782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694230/extras/eff4238cd08dfba998b958fc9b7cb58f.mp4?t=1767451782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Select your team</h2>Pick from one of three specialized ninja teams that best suit your playstyle. Every ninja has a unique skillset that offers a new way to play out fights.<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the wilderness</h2>Navigate through procedurally-generated nature dungeons in four different zones in order to seal away the spirits guarding them. Avoid traps and collect treasure along the way.<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight monsters</h2>Shinobi Saga features interactive turn-based combat. Each enemy has a unique attack pattern - learning how to adapt to them is crucial for success.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694230/extras/bb4c810ca26a6c3cc0d3d27ebff882da.poster.avif?t=1767451782\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694230/extras/bb4c810ca26a6c3cc0d3d27ebff882da.webm?t=1767451782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694230/extras/bb4c810ca26a6c3cc0d3d27ebff882da.mp4?t=1767451782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Choose your Ninja team and embark on a quest through the wilderness to seal away the spirits of evil and save your village. Fight through procedurally-generated nature dungeons in turn-based battles driven by action commands. Collect pearls during your runs and spend them in the village to unlock new teams, upgrades, and information about the monsters you face.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694230/extras/eff4238cd08dfba998b958fc9b7cb58f.poster.avif?t=1767451782\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694230/extras/eff4238cd08dfba998b958fc9b7cb58f.webm?t=1767451782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694230/extras/eff4238cd08dfba998b958fc9b7cb58f.mp4?t=1767451782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Select your team</h2>Pick from one of three specialized ninja teams that best suit your playstyle. Every ninja has a unique skillset that offers a new way to play out fights.<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the wilderness</h2>Navigate through procedurally-generated nature dungeons in four different zones in order to seal away the spirits guarding them. Avoid traps and collect treasure along the way.<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight monsters</h2>Shinobi Saga features interactive turn-based combat. Each enemy has a unique attack pattern - learning how to adapt to them is crucial for success.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694230/extras/bb4c810ca26a6c3cc0d3d27ebff882da.poster.avif?t=1767451782\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/